Qu'est-ce que c'est la vie, chaton? (English: &quot;What is life, Kitten?&quot;), is the third EP released of MGMT, and their first live EP.

In October 2010, MGMT gave two concerts in Paris at the Bataclan (7th, 8th and 9th). Five of the songs played were released on this EP.

The EP is a digital download on iTunes and Amazon.
